{"tid":2443856,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"男學生「和你Shop」藏伸縮棍被控管有攻擊性武器罪  開審前罪還柙候判","createTime":"2021-03-12T10:00:39.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-12T11:49:18.000Z","uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"d58663bf56762d3ac1d731517a9447c220ab3a7d","tid":2443856,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-12T10:00:39.000Z","msg":"觀塘去年2月有「和你Shop」活動，呼籲眾人毋忘元朗7.21事件發生7個月。18歲學生當日因背包藏有一支伸縮棍被捕，原定今於觀塘裁判法院受審，但他於開審前認罪。辯方透露被告自小患有過度活躍症，亦因家境不佳需入住寄養家庭。惟縱然被告天生條件不如他人，但也「冇影響佢作為一個人嘅本質」。辯方又形容被告努力克服先天障礙，更在體育方面頗有成就，望法庭輕判。裁判官押後案件至本月26日，等候索取<span class=\"red\">更生中心及勞教中心報告</span>後判刑，被告須即時還柙。<br />\n<br />\n莫官認為控罪嚴重，但考慮被告初犯，過往亦無刑事定罪記錄，聽取求情後決定先索取更生中心及勞教中心報告，再作判刑，其間被告須還柙。"},{"pid":"b18feef25e8bdffcc295c72cad8a48bef747dc7c","tid":2443856,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-12T10:00:42.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210312/BTA5S45MW5BP7KTHCLWMHFG2KE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210312%2FBTA5S45MW5BP7KTHCLWMHFG2KE%2F&d=RGPktlJYpqjIeXpZRAkgw9C8ckn1nBU%2Fwr2%2FVciPwp8%3D&h=1cf643e2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210312%2FBTA5S45MW5BP7KTHCLWMHFG2KE%2F&h=20f099b2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210312/BTA5S45MW5BP7KTHCLWMHFG2KE/</a>"},{"pid":"7c9299e53d7ddbeedfbefddf3a79b8e3f46e4761","tid":2443856,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-12T10:02:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/20201228-42_30p5q_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2F20201228-42_30p5q_1200x0.png&h=ea7f6def&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1e9b7a50e2079b17f0376d1dbab3cc4b4253a657","tid":2443856,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-12T10:09:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets